reviewText: Awful, awful film. The snowboarding shots are pretty good, but no plot and terrible acting...don't waste your time.
I couldn't make it past ten minutes into it. This has low budget trash written all over it. It may be funny, but getting teeth pulled waiting for funny isn't my idea of a good time.

This is the sequel to Shred and even at the start of this movie, the title is Shred II. So I'm confused by the name Revenge of the Boarding School Dropouts. In addition, there is like a 5 second delay between the sound and frame, so it's just awkward to watch when the voices don't line up.
this movie has no plot it just a movie that you watch only if your drunk cause other wise you won't laugh at any of the jokes. in short to enjoy it turn off your brain and you might laugh
This was a great movie. The movie was shipped on time and the quality was perfect when we received it. it was brand new and in packaging. There were no problems at all.
